    "help_body": "<h2>How to Play</h2><p>Fill the entire 8×8 board with 11 tiles. Three grey tiles are already placed — arrange the remaining 8 colored tiles to fill every empty cell.</p><h3>Place a Tile</h3><ul><li><strong>Drag &amp; drop</strong> a tile from the piece tray onto the board.</li><li>Or <strong>tap</strong> a tile to select it (highlighted in yellow), then <strong>tap an empty cell</strong> on the board to place it.</li></ul><h3>Rotate a Tile</h3><ul><li><strong>Tap</strong> an already-selected tile again to rotate it 90°.</li></ul><h3>Remove a Tile</h3><ul><li><strong>Drag</strong> a placed tile off the board to return it to the tray.</li><li>Or <strong>tap</strong> a placed tile on the board to pick it back up.</li></ul><h3>Controls</h3><ul><li><kbd>#</kbd> + <kbd>Go</kbd> — jump to a specific puzzle.</li><li><kbd>Random</kbd> — load a random puzzle.</li><li><kbd>Hint</kbd> — reveal the correct position of one unplaced tile.</li></ul><p><em>Every puzzle has a solution. Take your time — this is about thinking, not speed.</em></p>",
